HOW TO INSTALL THE PCA VISUALISATION APP:
1. Download the three files.
2. Add the download location as the directory path.
3. Open and run PCA_Visual_Base.mat
4. The app will now appear in a separate window.

HOW TO USE:
You have two handles on the sliding bars corresponding to the x- and y- viewpoint.
The viewpoint is then visualised in the two plots with the resulting loading vectors on the bottom right.
